   MUTCD Field Office Training

   The Federal Highway Administration (FHWA) has presented the MUTCD
   Training to the following:
     * FHWA Resource Centers (see Who's Who)
     * FHWA Division Offices (see Who's Who)
     * State Highway Departments (see Who's Who)
     * Local Technical Assistance Program (LTAP) Offices
     * American Traffic Safety Services Association (ATSSA)

   The MUTCD training is conducted through the use of Powerpoint slides.
   The Powerpoint slides are available for public use are linked below:
     * Side-by-Side Comparison of the 1988 and 2000 Editions
     * 90-Minute Presentation
     * 4-Hour Presentation
     * 8-Hour Presentation
